"``<time>`` que facilitan la comprensión del contenido."

#: ../../htmlfaq.rst:178
msgid ""
"The ``<canvas>`` tag, which supports a powerful drawing API, reducing the"
" need for server-generated images to present data graphically."
msgstr ""
